REMARK_EN: Due to the amount of siltation and its effect, water level and discharge data is considered poor quality from March 1 to March 28 and fair from March 28 to June 11.

Due to measures in place to limit the spread of coronavirus, regular visits to this station were reduced or no longer conducted throughout the period of March 2020 to October 2020. This may have impacted data quality in Stage.Working and Discharge.Working.
Due measures in place to limit the spread of the coronavirus, regular visits to this station were reduced throughout 2020.  This may have impacted data quality.
